title: 288. American Revival Part 3 Ft. Eric Greitens
itunes:title: 288. American Revival Part 3 Ft. Eric Greitens
description: In today's episode, Andy & DJ are joined in the studio by former Missouri Governor and Senatorial Candidate Eric Greitens. They talk about Eric’s story of how he got started with humanitarian public service, why individual accountability & personal excellence are the stepping stones for a prosperous America, and how to think critically to take better decisions for the future of your community and for the future of America.
